# VPS Update / Deploy

When the user asks how to update the VPS or deploy the app, give this command sequence (run from local or from the VPS after SSH).

## From local (then on VPS)

1. SSH into the VPS:
   ```bash
   ssh tas
   ```

2. Go to project and app directory:
   ```bash
   cd /home/brandon/Task_aversion_system
   cd task_aversion_app
   ```

3. Pull latest and restart the app:
   ```bash
   git pull origin main
   sudo systemctl restart task-aversion-app
   ```

## One-liner (after SSH)

From `/home/brandon/Task_aversion_system/task_aversion_app`:

```bash
git pull origin main; sudo systemctl restart task-aversion-app
```

Host alias: `tas`. Service: `task-aversion-app`.
